                                        <div class="std"><!--<p></p>--></div><div class="desire-for-bringing">
<h2>desire for bringing high quality products</h2>
<p>Drapes 4 Show is a Los Angeles based manufacturer and importer of textiles suited for many different industries. Our core values bring us closer to our customers and drive us to innovate.&nbsp;</p>
<iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/250156796" width="640" height="360" allowfullscreen webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen></iframe>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div><div class="research-container">
    <div class="other-stories-wrapper">
<div class="our-other-stories"><span>research and development for textile products</span>
<p>Drapes 4 Show chooses to invest its profits and efforts more into our manufacturing processes. While marketing and sales efforts are important, we find that our investments better serve our customers and ourselves by making sure we operate in the most efficient manner to deliver a cost effective quality product on time and as ordered.</p>
</div>
