<div class="our-other-stories"><span> Our Story </span>
<p>Drapes 4 Show's 30 employees design and sew tablecloths, napkins, table draping fabrics, backdrops and other products for hotels, convention centers and hospitality industry clients. It's a lucrative niche that brought in $3.6 million in sales in 2007, but it began in an unlikely fashion.</p>
